{"tid":2384581,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"地盤工性侵女童判144個月　警察性侵女童判46個月","createTime":"2021-01-28T15:30:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T06:12:39.000Z","uid":261647,"like":153,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"9de36468f1d9d1b58300bbcdab63fe0d28d29ce4","tid":2384581,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T15:30:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/joseph.lo.1840/posts/3405789692893315\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fjoseph.lo.1840%2Fposts%2F3405789692893315&d=YX1qj72dVL8lCt3J0nVEUnwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=7ccb78c1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/joseph.lo.1840/posts/3405789692893315</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/byRM4Mh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbyRM4Mh.jpg&h=853b6457&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作者：Joseph Lo<br />\n<br />\n地盤工性侵犯3名12至23歲的女網友判144個月<br />\n警察性侵至少 6 名年 11 至 14 歲的女童就判46個月<br />\n<br />\n從案情中已可見，涉案警員的行為已為強姦罪行；但是， 律政司只控告肇事警員：<br />\n1.兩項向十六歲以下兒童作出猥褻行為；<br />\n2.一項管有兒童色情物品；<br />\n3.三項非禮；及<br />\n4.兩項非法性交罪。<br />\n<br />\n此案明顯牽涉了不自願、威迫、莽顧意願下發生性行為等原則。明確地，律政司連風化案都要圖添政治色彩，此舉如同大聲告訴世人假若香港警察強姦女性不幸被發現，仍有律政司在背後撐腰，「坐都坐少啲」。<br />\n<br />\n今天律政司只是執行政權殺人意志的劊子手，眼中沒有公道，更沒有義理。"},{"pid":"ec90b13d56f379020b0083c81ffb87c0aa39fa67","tid":2384581,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T15:31:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d38baa4fd4c404cd6868515d34e7d146581503a8","tid":2384581,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T15:31:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3e82dc651c799c63fda7df130f865085986f111","tid":2384581,"uid":231480,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"